- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper focuses on the development of an autonomous driving system for a racecar, which falls under the domain of robotics. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper mentions the use of LiDAR and vision-based cone detection for perception, which are both computer vision techniques. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper mentions the use of a model predictive control algorithm for optimization, which is a common AI technique. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the control aspect of the autonomous driving system, which falls under the domain of systems and control. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): Although not explicitly mentioned, the use of machine learning techniques for perception and control is common in autonomous driving systems, making this a possible sub-category as well.
